---
// Features bento grid — porting markup verbatim from the original design.
---

<section id="fitur">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">★ Fitur Utama</span>
      <h2>Semua yang Dibutuhkan Website Sekolah Modern</h2>
      <p>Sistem lengkap yang dirancang khusus untuk kebutuhan sekolah Indonesia — dari berita harian hingga pengelolaan jurusan.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bento">
      <article class="bento-card feature-tall reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="M8 21h8"></path>
            <path d="M12 17v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Tampilan Modern &amp; Responsif</h3>
        <p>Desain premium yang tampil sempurna di HP, tablet, dan komputer. Template terpilih bisa dikustomisasi warna, logo, dan konten sesuai identitas sekolah Anda.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-devices">
            <div class="feat-laptop">
              <div class="bar full"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="width:40%"></div>
              <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:4px;margin-top:auto">
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feat-phone">
              <div class="bar accent"></div>
              <div class="bar"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="width:40%"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface-2);height:30px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:auto"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface-2);height:30px;border-radius:4px"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-wide reveal">
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:center;height:100%">
          <div>
            <div class="ico">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path>
                <path d="M17 21H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"></path>
                <line x1="9" y1="13" x2="15" y2="13"></line>
                <line x1="9" y1="17" x2="13" y2="17"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 style="margin-top:14px">Kelola Berita &amp; Artikel Mudah</h3>
            <p>Rich-text editor dengan draft, revisi, dan jadwal publikasi. Buat berita sekolah kapan saja — tidak perlu coding sama sekali.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-editor">
            <div class="toolbar">
              <span>B</span><span>I</span><span>U</span><span>"</span><span style="margin-left:auto">📷</span>
            </div>
            <div class="line w-1"></div>
            <div class="line w-2"></div>
            <div class="line w-3"></div>
            <div class="line w-2"></div>
            <div class="line cursor"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Galeri Foto Sekolah</h3>
        <p>Upload langsung dari dashboard, atur urutan, tambah keterangan. Tampil otomatis di website.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-gallery">
            <div class="ph big"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sistem Hak Akses (RBAC)</h3>
        <p>Tiga level akses dengan batas yang jelas — konten aman, kontrol penuh.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-roles">
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Super Admin <span class="badge">Full Access</span></div>
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Editor <span class="badge">Publish</span></div>
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Kontributor <span class="badge">Draft</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-sm reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Profil Guru</h3>
        <p>Tampilkan tenaga pendidik dengan slider profesional.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-sm reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Menu Navigasi Dinamis</h3>
        <p>Drag &amp; drop susun ulang menu tanpa minta developer.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-sm reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Performa &amp; SEO Ready</h3>
        <div class="feat-perf" style="margin-top:6px">
          <div class="gauge" style="--val:98"><span class="v">98<small>Score</small></span></div>
          <p style="font-size:13px">Next.js, SSR, dan optimasi gambar bawaan. Load cepat, siap muncul di Google.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 21h18"></path>
            <path d="M5 21V7l8-4 8 4v14"></path>
            <path d="M9 9h1"></path><path d="M9 13h1"></path><path d="M9 17h1"></path>
            <path d="M14 9h1"></path><path d="M14 13h1"></path><path d="M14 17h1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Profil Institusional Lengkap</h3>
        <p>Visi, Misi, Sejarah Sekolah, Prakata Kepala Sekolah, hingga detail Jurusan/Program Keahlian — semua dari panel admin.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card feature-sm reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Penyimpanan Cloud</h3>
        <p>Media tersimpan di Amazon S3, dioptimasi otomatis, tidak membebani hosting.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="bento-note reveal">
      💡 <strong>Butuh fitur tambahan?</strong> Kami open request — ceritakan kebutuhan spesifik sekolah Anda saat konsultasi.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
